Package: shinybrain
Title: Static Analysis and App Brain Export for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("ShinyBrain", "Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "prigasgenthian48@gmail.com")
Description: Statically analyzes Shiny application codebases without running
    the app. Produces an interactive dependency graph and a portable structured
    export (the App Brain) that can be shared with LLMs or agents. Covers
    reactive expressions, observers, modules, helper functions, and sourced
    files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    tibble (>= 3.0.0),
    rlang (>= 1.0.0),
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    jsonlite
Config/testthat/edition: 3
